string-array.name: cn_terms_privacy_msg
string-array.item: "1. All the collected data will be encrypted during the transmission from this product to ASUS. 2. ASUS will not disclose, share or transfer any personal data collected from you to any third parties without your consent. 3. Please visit System > About phone > Privacy settings in this product at any time to enable/disable the sharing of your personal data with ASUS. 4. If you would like to know more about how ASUS protects your privacy, please visit [[ASUS privacy policy]] for further information."
